---
---

<section id="faq" class="py-24 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif text-slate-900 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">Everything you need to know about our local SEO service.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden" open>
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer list-none p-6 text-slate-900">
          <span>How long until I see results?</span>
          <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
            <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="text-slate-600 px-6 pb-6">
          <p>Local SEO is a long-term strategy, but you'll typically start seeing movement in your Google Maps rankings within the first 30-60 days. Organic search rankings take a bit longer, usually 3-6 months depending on your competition. The automated review system starts working immediately.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer list-none p-6 text-slate-900">
          <span>Do I need to spend money on ads?</span>
          <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
            <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="text-slate-600 px-6 pb-6">
          <p>No. Our entire focus is on organic visibility—getting you to the top of Google Maps and regular search results without paying for clicks. Once you rank organically, that traffic is free.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer list-none p-6 text-slate-900">
          <span>What if I'm already with another SEO company?</span>
          <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
            <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="text-slate-600 px-6 pb-6">
          <p>We can seamlessly transition your campaigns. We'll do a full audit of what they've done, keep the good stuff, and fix what's holding you back. We specialize specifically in local service businesses, which gives us an edge over generalist agencies.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer list-none p-6 text-slate-900">
          <span>Is there a lock-in contract?</span>
          <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
            <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="text-slate-600 px-6 pb-6">
          <p>We ask for an initial 3-month commitment because SEO takes time to build momentum. After that, it's strictly month-to-month. We want to keep you by delivering results, not with a legal contract.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
      
      <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer list-none p-6 text-slate-900">
          <span>What exactly do I get for $500/month?</span>
          <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
            <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="text-slate-600 px-6 pb-6">
          <p>You get our complete Local Dominance system: full Google Business Profile optimisation and management, on-page SEO for your website, our automated 5-star review collection system, local directory citations, and monthly performance reporting.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
